You just grabbed all the mail from your mailbox.   You want to go through it all, and decide what to do with each piece of mail.
Write the pseudo code for your process of going through the mail.


for each piece of mail...


if JUNK mail
   throw in trash...

if BILLS
  set mail to the side 
  else open mail and pay BILLS now...

if LETTER FROM PARENTS
   sit down and open immediately...
else open when you have time...

If MAGAZINES
   check for coupons
   else put to the side for reading material
      
      else throw away as junk